# Exercise Evaluator

## üöÄ Description
This Fitness App is a real-time web application designed to track body posture and evaluate exercises using computer vision. It helps users perform workouts correctly by analyzing their movements through a webcam and providing instant visual feedback.

## üõ† Tech Stack
Frontend: React.js, JavaScript, HTML, CSS
Computer Vision: MediaPipe Pose
3D / Visualization: Three.js
Build Tool: Vite
Version Control: Git & GitHub

## ‚ú® Features
Real-time body pose detection using webcam
Exercise posture analysis and visualization
Interactive UI for fitness tracking
3D pose rendering for better movement understanding
Lightweight and browser-based (no external hardware required)

## ‚öôÔ∏è How to Run
Prerequisites
Node.js installed
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/fitness-app.git
# Navigate to project folder
cd fitness-app
# Install dependencies
npm install
# Start the development server
npm run dev

open your broswer and visit 
http://localhost:5173

